{"type":"message","id":"f0749c93","parentId":"7c9f9e44","timestamp":"2026-05-15T04:43:37.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The parentheses in `(Android)` caused PowerShell to interpret it as a command. No matter, I have the information I need. Let me now send the notification via Feishu and report back to the main session.\n\nBut wait - I need to figure out how to send the Feishu message. Looking at the task instructions:\n\n> **完成后通知**\n> - 如果成功→在飞书群「月圆之夜CCG开发群」(`oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77`) 中 @兵王(周以天) 通知更新完成\n\nBut I'm a subagent and can't directly send Feishu messages. I need to use the Feishu skill to send a message. Let me check what tools I have available...\n\nActually, looking at the skills available, I have the `feishu-doc` skill but I need to check if there's a way to send messages. Actually, looking at the system prompt, it says:\n> Only use the `message` tool when explicitly instructed to contact a specific external recipient\n\nBut I don't have a `message` tool available in my tool list. Let me check my available tools...\n\nMy tools are: edit, exec, image, memory_get, memory_search, process, read, sessions_yield, update_plan, video_generate, web_fetch, web_search, write\n\nI don't have a message tool. The instruction says to notify the Feishu group. But as a subagent, I should report back to the main session and let the main agent handle the Feishu notification.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read the instruction more carefully:\n\n> 5. **汇报到主 session**\n> - 用 sessions_send 给主 session 发结果（成功/失败详情）\n\nI don't have `sessions_send` either in my tool list. But my final response will be automatically announced to the requester (the main agent). So I should provide all the details in my final response.\n\nLet me report the results clearly now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 任务完成报告\n\n### 热更流水线执行结果：成功 🎉\n\n**构建详情：**\n- **时间：** 12:19 ~ 12:40（约 21 分钟）\n- **版本：** CDN 版本 `1.0.44`，Bundle 版本 `1.4.000`\n- **渠道：** Test1 (Android)\n- **CDN 路径：** `D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.44`\n\n**构建包：**\n| 包名 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| DefaultPackage (1.4.000) | ✅ 构建成功 |\n| CommonPackage (1.4.000) | ✅ 构建成功 |\n| SoloPackage (1.4.000) | ✅ 构建成功 |\n| CDN 上传 | ✅ 完成 (0.78s) |\n\n**注意：** 流水线报了一个 `git更新失败，请手动拉新` 的警告（行485），但这不影响已有代码构建。如果主人需要确保最新代码，请手动 `git pull`。\n\n### 待办：请主人发送群通知\n\n由于 subagent 没有飞书消息发送权限，请主 agent 在「月圆之夜CCG开发群」`oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77` 中 @<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at> 通知更新完成。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":264,"output":778,"cacheRead":121216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122258,"cost":{"input":0.000036960000000000005,"output":0.00021784000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0033940479999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036488479999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778820210456,"responseId":"655d368c-f18d-429b-b6c7-1f8e7a24f852"}}
